    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Oligopeptide-107 sh-Oligopeptide-1 is a single chain synthetic fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sh-Oligopeptide-1 and Oligopeptide-107. The fused peptide contains 67 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
